item.description:
Hi Westport Boston Terrier Meetup Members
We are going to try to meet at the town beach!For those people who don't know the beach we can meet at my home in Westport and then head for the beach!
If it is too cold we have an alternate meetup at Dighton Rock State Park!
Hope to see yoy on April 11th
Linda and Bob
20 Truman St
Westport,Ma
Ps-You will get an email about location of this meetup!
